---
title: Shawarma Meatballs with Bulgur and Sumac Veggies
description: Meatballs aren’t just an Italian-American or Swedish thing. Here, we’re introducing a version that incorporates the spices of the Middle East. Accompanied by hearty bulgur and tender roasted veggies, these little baubles will convince you that meatballs are good with just about anything.

***Please note that this recipe may be packaged with samples that contain peanuts and soy.***
